      description_md: "The FEMA-managed National Flood Insurance Program (NFIP) enables homeowners, business owners and renters in participating communities to purchase federally backed flood insurance. This dataset includes insurance claims and amounts paid for flood damage to buildings and their contents, aggregated by census tracts, counties and states.\n"
      verticals: ["Environment"]
    },
