      description_md: "Produces yearly estimates of the population for the United States, its states, counties, cities, and towns, as well as for the Commonwealth of Puerto Rico and its municipios. Data Commons imports the total population estimate data for the U.S. at the state, county, and city levels.\n"
      verticals: ["Demographics"]
